    <div class="pro" style="flex: 1; max-width: 400px;">
      <img src="/productimage/p7.png" alt="Local Products" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 10px;" />
      <div class="des" style="padding: 10px 0;">
        <h5>Empowering Local Women</h5>
        <p>
          Each textile supports women weavers and keeps Bhutan’s rich cultural heritage alive. When you shop with us, you're part of that story.
